Q) Puzzle Description : A man fell in a 30 meter deep well, in one day he climbs 4 meters up, and slips 3 meters down. How many days would it take for him, to come out of the well?



Answer:- On day 1 4 meters up and 3 meter down in this way only climbs for 1 day
on 2nd day another 4 meter and slips 3 meter down and total distance 2 meters
on day 26 and 27, 4 meters again. on 27th day man climbs 30 metersand on 27th day man not slips.
